{"tid":1372554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Online]關於撤退嘅問題","createTime":"2019-07-27T12:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:02:56.000Z","uid":25169,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca197226c436ec9fa10d19081e21644f80fbd47","tid":1372554,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"其實可以重新討論點樣分工<br />\n冷氣軍師負責<br />\n(1)update資訊同<br />\n(2)提供撤退路線<br />\n<br />\n唔好成日話幾點走，可以建議短時間內走，等前線判斷<br />\ne.g. 幾點有清場，幾時會有白衫<br />\n<br />\n大家都係新手，記住要團結升lv。或者中間可能有豬隊友，但我地可以點醒佢，隊友係要互助cover，取長補短。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92163af9e31406bd1ad6726895829bd3be0bc03","tid":1372554,"uid":259928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n每次遊行之前麻煩同我推一推俾人睇，一個727發現但係一直都有既現象<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372164</a>"},{"pid":"4889be5e198612a54fef36ac1391dca8da22af3c","tid":1372554,"uid":20059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好比人分化  快入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372487</a><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"6c3ad8969fea5afa92142bbc428297f58836d2e7","tid":1372554,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b92163af9e31406bd1ad6726895829bd3be0bc03","tid":1372554,"uid":259928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n每次遊行之前麻煩同我推一推俾人睇，一個727發現但係一直都有既現象<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372164</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f1ccc777c4cbde4b6b1e52cd16ffc2fbb9d5ce9","tid":1372554,